<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Hi,</p>

<p>add static method:  Zend_Db::listSupportedAdapters(void)
return array of all database adapters which supported by Zend_Framework and installed php</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
array(
  '' =&gt; ''
  [, '' =&gt; ''[, ...]]
)
</code></pre>

<p>e.g:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
array(
  'pdo_mysql' =&gt; 'MySQL over PDO',
  'pdo_sqlite' =&gt; 'SQLite over PDO',
  'oracle&gt;'  =&gt; 'Oracle',
  'mysqli' =&gt; 'MySQLi',
  'db2' =&gt; 'DB2',
)
</code></pre>

